casebody.data:
Robert L. HENRY, petitioner,
v.
FLORIDA. No. 13-9192 (13A938). Supreme Court of the United States March 20, 2014.

Case below, 134 So.3d 938.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by her referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Florida denied.
